  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Exporting active substance manufactured in the UK in a no deal scenario
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Information on the ‘Written Confirmation’ process, for active substances manufactured in the United Kingdom (UK), that will be adopted in a no deal scenario.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

